version_description:
- updated vehicle database

- added precision for parameters (PIDs) - digits after the decimal point, in addition to min/max limit

- fixed bug of lost min/max settings entered by user (values entered prior to 1.3.2 may still be lost...)

- fixed visual problems in Dashboard

- Added two new sizes for gauges ("very big" and "huge")

- Increased connection timeout (helps in case of very slow WiFi adapters)

- Vehicle database update
- Fixed incorrect work with HS2/HS3/MS CAN bus on ELM327 adapters with HS/MS CAN switch
- Added new setting - CSV delimiter (can be selected between semicolon and comma)
